# Portfolio Website - Aman Kumar

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This project showcases my skills, experience, and projects in web development.

## 🚀 Live Demo
Check out the live version of my portfolio: [Portfolio Website](#)

## 📌 Features
- Responsive and interactive UI
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Projects showcase with descriptions and links
- Contact form for easy communication
- Tech stack details and skills section
- Blog or additional achievements section (if included)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Other Tools**: Git, GitHub, VS Code

## 📂 Project Structure
```
Portfolio-website-Aman/
│── index.html         # Main HTML file
│── css/               # Stylesheets
│── js/                # JavaScript files
│── assets/            # Images and media
│── README.md
```

## 🎨 UI & Design
The website follows a modern, clean design with responsive elements. It adapts to different screen sizes for an optimal experience on all devices.

## 🖥️ Setup & Installation
To run this project locally, follow these steps:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Aman-Kumar778/Portfolio-website-Aman.git
   ```
2. Navigate to the project folder:
   ```bash
   cd Portfolio-website-Aman
   ```
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

